thread.title: BRIEF-Alkemy Unit Signs Agreement With Nelt Co. For Establishment Of JV

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Alkemy Unit Signs Agreement With Nelt Co. For Establishment Of JV

organizations.name: brief-alkemy unit signs agreement with nelt co

text:
Feb 9 (Reuters) - Alkemy Spa:
* SAYS ITS UNIT ALKEMY SEE (SOUTH EAST EUROPE) SIGNED AGREEMENT WITH NELT CO. DOO FOR ESTABLISHMENT OF JV
* SAYS 51% OF JV SHARE CAPITAL WILL BE HELD BY ALKEMY SEE AND 49% BY NELT CO. DOO
* SAYS THROUGH JV ALKEMY ACQUIRES 100% OF TAKO LAKO SHOP D.O.O., A COMPANY BELONGING TO NELT GROUP Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
